1
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:14,840
[Chae Jong Hyeok as Kim Min Joon]

2
00:00:15,540 --> 00:00:19,230
[Seong Seung Ha as Choi Jin Hwan]

3
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:34,660
[Business as Usual]

4
00:00:55,070 --> 00:00:57,250
<i>Make sure to eat well.</i>

5
00:01:02,180 --> 00:01:05,280
<i>Okay, I will.</i>

6
00:01:42,310 --> 00:01:44,250
<i>We're having a second round now.</i>

7
00:01:48,550 --> 00:01:51,210
<i>Okay. Have fun.</i>

8
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,270
Choi Jin Hwan,

9
00:02:14,270 --> 00:02:15,780
are you that happy?

10
00:02:15,780 --> 00:02:18,620
Yes. I'm so happy.

11
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:22,730
What do you like so much about them?

12
00:02:23,510 --> 00:02:27,890
I strangely like everything about them.

13
00:02:27,890 --> 00:02:30,310
You've been smiling all day.

14
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:32,240
I can't stand it.

15
00:02:33,620 --> 00:02:37,930
You said you didn't confess your love properly.

16
00:02:37,930 --> 00:02:40,310
Do they feel the same way as you do?

17
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:44,800
Sorry.

18
00:02:49,250 --> 00:02:50,990
Yes, Honey.

19
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:54,770
I should head back now. Yeah.

20
00:02:57,980 --> 00:03:00,570
Geon Joo, call my phone.

21
00:03:01,540 --> 00:03:04,460
Where did you lose it?

22
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:10,270
<i>The phone is powered off...</i>

23
00:03:10,270 --> 00:03:12,900
It says your phone is off.

24
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:14,710
Didn't you say you ran out of battery?

25
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:16,400
Yes.

26
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,340
Maybe you left it at the previous place.

27
00:03:18,340 --> 00:03:20,780
I saw you asking them to charge it.

28
00:03:23,510 --> 00:03:25,590
I'll have to get going now.

29
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,560
[Are you drunk?]

30
00:03:45,690 --> 00:03:48,800
[Where are you?]

31
00:03:58,140 --> 00:04:02,510
<i>The phone is powered off. You'll be connected...</i>

32
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:16,160
<i>You think living this way is acceptable?</i>

33
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:20,250
<i>What would your late mother think?</i>

34
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,970
<i>Min Joon!</i>

35
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:46,080
My phone died, so I asked them to charge it,

36
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:48,270
but it wasn't charged.

37
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:52,510
Sorry. You must've worried.

38
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:59,270
I was going to call the police
because I couldn't reach you.

39
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:01,020
Stop joking.

40
00:06:01,780 --> 00:06:03,460
I'm glad you found it.

41
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:05,280
I'll go home now.

42
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,790
Let's go together. You came this far.

43
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,460
No.

44
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:16,690
I'm a bit tired today.

45
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,880
While I couldn't reach you,

46
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:32,140
I only thought about contacting you.

47
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:36,870
I didn't want you to misunderstand again.

48
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,930
Min Joon,

49
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:44,290
remember what you said last time?

50
00:06:45,970 --> 00:06:49,980
You said you were scared
because you liked me too much.

51
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:54,650
Thinking now,

52
00:06:54,650 --> 00:06:58,230
I think I was afraid of liking someone

53
00:06:58,230 --> 00:07:00,330
sincerely then.

54
00:07:03,670 --> 00:07:06,560
I never got to confess my love properly.

55
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,540
So, I'll finally tell you now.

56
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:13,040
Kim Min Joon,

57
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:16,130
go out with me.

58
00:07:17,860 --> 00:07:21,120
♫ <i>This morning, as I opened my eyes</i> ♫

59
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:25,010
♫ <i>I thought of your face the first thing, as usual</i> ♫

60
00:07:25,990 --> 00:07:27,890
You know, too.

61
00:07:29,220 --> 00:07:32,920
You and I are really incompatible.

62
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,960
That's normal.

63
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:37,380
And we know what the issue is now.

64
00:07:37,380 --> 00:07:38,690
We can be clear with each other.

65
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:41,110
We'll be clear what we like and don't like.

66
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:45,280
We'll fight and get tired again.

67
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:48,440
And we'll be worn out each time.

68
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,110
You don't know that.

69
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:51,360
If we work hard for each other-

70
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:54,680
You think everything would be possible now.

71
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:58,370
But what if...

72
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:03,620
I keep bringing up the past and

73
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:05,950
ask you why you acted that way angrily?

74
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:07,270
I can just let you-

75
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:10,470
Similar things keep happening.

76
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:14,300
No one would be okay with that.

77
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:17,820
And what if...

78
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:21,560
you keep doing that to me?

79
00:08:23,910 --> 00:08:25,830
I know myself well.

80
00:08:26,770 --> 00:08:28,750
I won't be able to stand it.

81
00:08:34,070 --> 00:08:37,320
You know how it'd end.

82
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,400
And I know, too.

83
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:43,450
Yes, that can be.

84
00:08:43,450 --> 00:08:46,100
We could fight more if we get back together.

85
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:47,830
But Min Joon,

86
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:53,540
when could we date like this again, if not now?

87
00:08:54,430 --> 00:08:58,020
I know everything, and I'm getting sick of everything.

88
00:08:58,820 --> 00:09:02,620
But I want to believe you'd be different.

89
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:07,530
How many times will that happen again in life?

90
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:13,220
Choi Jin Hwan.

91
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:19,230
First love needs to be left as a memory.

92
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:22,030
No, right now is important to me.

93
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,750
How do you feel now?

94
00:09:24,370 --> 00:09:26,380
I know you like me.

95
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:31,720
Stop.

96
00:09:35,870 --> 00:09:38,310
Please let me be free now.

97
00:09:43,540 --> 00:09:45,040
Please...

98
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:50,070
just get out of my sight.

99
00:09:52,970 --> 00:09:54,750
Do you mean that?

100
00:09:57,430 --> 00:09:58,800
Yes.

101
00:10:01,110 --> 00:10:08,900
♫ <i>Those words are such precious feelings</i> ♫

102
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:13,320
♫ <i>You made me realize that</i> ♫

103
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:17,480
♫ <i>I love you</i> ♫

104
00:10:19,850 --> 00:10:23,720
♫ <i>I love you</i> ♫

105
00:10:56,300 --> 00:11:10,040
♫ <i>Do you know how much I've been looking for you?</i> ♫

106
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:13,600
♫ <i>In the empty room,</i> ♫

107
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:24,080
♫ <i>I was left alone and beyond the time that I had lost</i> ♫

108
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:31,100
♫ <i>It must be my selfish desire</i> ♫

109
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:37,040
♫ <i>The past that I gave up on</i> ♫

110
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:43,640
[Episode 6: To the Subordinates
Who Are Bad at Relationships]

111
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,560
It came out nice, right?

112
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:48,850
It's not bad.

113
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:50,260
Hello.

114
00:11:50,260 --> 00:11:52,020
Hello.

115
00:11:53,020 --> 00:11:55,070
It's finally finished.

116
00:11:55,070 --> 00:11:57,460
Everyone worked so hard.

117
00:11:57,460 --> 00:11:59,720
When is Jin Hwan coming?

118
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:02,280
Looks like he's been sick for days.

119
00:12:03,070 --> 00:12:06,740
He must've worried about the project and speech.

120
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:09,150
I guess so.

121
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:12,540
Let's work hard together, then.

122
00:12:12,540 --> 00:12:14,120
Fighting.

123
00:12:20,980 --> 00:12:25,800
<i>This book is for those who are inexperienced in love.</i>

124
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:29,830
<i>It's a book with tips you need in relationships.</i>

125
00:12:29,830 --> 00:12:32,760
<i>Of course, these tips are important,</i>

126
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:35,330
<i>but the most important thing is</i>

127
00:12:35,330 --> 00:12:38,610
<i>expressing yourself to the other.</i>

128
00:12:38,610 --> 00:12:40,940
<i>Let's not forget that.</i>

129
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:07,370
You worked hard.

130
00:13:07,370 --> 00:13:09,910
You worked harder than me.

131
00:13:11,170 --> 00:13:12,720
Kim Min Joon.

132
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,010
Good morning.

133
00:13:14,010 --> 00:13:15,890
My hunch was correct, wasn't it?

134
00:13:15,890 --> 00:13:17,990
It hasn't been published, but it's so popular.

135
00:13:17,990 --> 00:13:19,670
Of course.

136
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:24,110
Our department should go out for dinner tonight.

137
00:13:24,110 --> 00:13:27,060
Director, let's go when Jin Hwan returns.

138
00:13:27,060 --> 00:13:28,360
Haven't you heard?

139
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,050
He's not working with us anymore.

140
00:13:30,050 --> 00:13:31,850
Pardon? Really?

141
00:13:31,850 --> 00:13:34,770
He was supposed to come to pack last night.

142
00:13:34,770 --> 00:13:36,570
You must've missed him.

143
00:13:37,260 --> 00:13:41,160
Anyway, prepare for the dinner tonight.

144
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:58,430
[Choi Jin Hwan]

145
00:14:04,740 --> 00:14:08,410
[Don't overdo it]

146
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:18,590
Did Jin Hwan really not say anything?

147
00:14:18,590 --> 00:14:20,080
No.

148
00:14:22,270 --> 00:14:24,440
That's too bad.

149
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:29,730
- Babe!
- Babe.

150
00:14:29,730 --> 00:14:31,040
What brings you here?

151
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:32,600
I came to talk to Min Joon.

152
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:36,620
What? I thought you came to see me.

153
00:14:36,620 --> 00:14:38,940
I'll pick you up later.

154
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:41,250
Let's get something tasty for dinner.

155
00:14:41,250 --> 00:14:42,930
Okay. Have a nice chat.

156
00:14:42,930 --> 00:14:44,600
Enjoy your meal.

157
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,120
Okay.

158
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:54,000
Min Joon, we meet again.

159
00:14:54,970 --> 00:14:56,540
I know.

160
00:15:00,190 --> 00:15:02,160
Things didn't work out, did it?

161
00:15:05,810 --> 00:15:08,700
I've known Jin Hwan for a long time.

162
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:12,630
I know what he's thinking just by seeing his face

163
00:15:12,630 --> 00:15:16,670
and what's going on when he can't be reached.

164
00:15:18,070 --> 00:15:20,730
So, tell me what's going on.

165
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:26,220
I wish Choi Jin Hwan the best.

166
00:15:26,980 --> 00:15:28,760
I want him to stop acting out

167
00:15:28,760 --> 00:15:30,230
and return to his father's company-

168
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:32,530
He's not acting out.

169
00:15:32,530 --> 00:15:35,540
He's trying to do things on his own.

170
00:15:35,540 --> 00:15:37,460
He's smart.

171
00:15:37,460 --> 00:15:39,980
He must have a plan, I'm sure.

172
00:15:39,980 --> 00:15:42,060
He's different than me.

173
00:15:43,060 --> 00:15:45,760
Whenever I'm with him, I feel anxious

174
00:15:46,450 --> 00:15:48,820
and I feel smaller.

175
00:15:51,130 --> 00:15:54,200
Doesn't it mean you like him that much?

176
00:15:56,770 --> 00:15:58,700
This isn't working.

177
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:02,740
He asked me not to tell you.

178
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:09,190
He's wrapping things up and moving abroad.

179
00:16:09,190 --> 00:16:10,550
What?

180
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:14,310
I'm not sure what you think of him,

181
00:16:15,540 --> 00:16:18,820
but he only thinks of you all the time.

182
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:23,210
So, shouldn't you face him for the last time?

183
00:16:23,210 --> 00:16:25,960
I can see it in your eyes, too.

184
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:28,200
You miss him.

185
00:16:33,590 --> 00:16:35,400
<i>You look tired.</i>

186
00:16:36,530 --> 00:16:38,280
<i>I drank.</i>

187
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:42,020
<i>With whom?</i>

188
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:43,890
<i>Did you sleep well?</i>

189
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:48,710
<i>Come on. Don't be sleazy.</i>

190
00:16:48,710 --> 00:16:50,320
<i>What did I do?</i>

191
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:55,500
<i>I also want to be free from those rules and tips</i>

192
00:16:55,500 --> 00:16:59,160
<i>and focus on my heart completely.</i>

193
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:05,000
<i>I lost you while goofing around then.</i>

194
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:09,260
<i>So, I want to make things right while I can.</i>

195
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:15,100
♫ <i>No matter what I write</i> ♫

196
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:18,760
♫ <i>I can't express it</i> ♫

197
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:21,350
♫ <i>The letter I couldn't send</i> ♫

198
00:17:21,350 --> 00:17:25,070
♫ <i>I love you</i> ♫

199
00:17:25,070 --> 00:17:32,780
♫ <i>Those words are so hard to say</i> ♫

200
00:17:32,780 --> 00:17:37,070
♫ <i>You made me realize that</i> ♫

201
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:41,350
♫ <i>I love you</i> ♫

202
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:48,460
Woo Hyeok,

203
00:17:49,180 --> 00:17:50,440
What?

204
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:51,880
Thank you...

205
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:54,160
for being honest with me.

206
00:17:55,170 --> 00:17:57,270
Thinking now,

207
00:17:58,180 --> 00:18:00,790
I've always been running away.

208
00:18:03,650 --> 00:18:05,250
Min Joon,

209
00:18:07,870 --> 00:18:10,430
his flight is leaving this evening.

210
00:18:12,210 --> 00:18:14,000
I told you, okay?

211
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:18,140
I should get going, too.

212
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:20,570
See you.

213
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:36,110
<i>The number you dialed does not exist.</i>

214
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,440
Director, something urgent came up.

215
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:45,520
Yes, I'll take the afternoon off.

216
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:47,250
I'm sorry.

217
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:28,500
♫ <i>If this is a dream, I hope I don't wake up</i> ♫

218
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:35,520
♫ <i>So, I could spend more time with you</i> ♫

219
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:40,450
♫ <i>I came too far</i> ♫

220
00:19:40,450 --> 00:19:44,010
♫ <i>It's too far away</i> ♫

221
00:19:44,010 --> 00:19:47,810
♫ <i>The countless words</i> ♫

222
00:19:50,800 --> 00:19:57,900
♫ <i>I try as hard as I can, but it's not getting any better</i> ♫

223
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:01,720
Choi Jin Hwan!

224
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:12,170
♫ <i>The countless breakups around me</i> ♫

225
00:20:12,170 --> 00:20:15,010
Choi Jin Hwan, what's with you?

226
00:20:15,010 --> 00:20:17,570
You changed your number and tried to disappear?

227
00:20:18,860 --> 00:20:21,630
The person I like wants me to disappear.

228
00:20:21,630 --> 00:20:23,490
It was the least I could do.

229
00:20:25,940 --> 00:20:27,830
You bastard.

230
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:31,690
Why did you come?

231
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:34,990
You and I...

232
00:20:34,990 --> 00:20:37,400
are really incompatible.

233
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:41,610
That's why I'll fight as many times as it takes.

234
00:20:44,190 --> 00:20:45,770
Even if you get tired

235
00:20:45,770 --> 00:20:49,410
and beg me to let go of you,

236
00:20:49,410 --> 00:20:52,430
I won't let go of you, okay?

237
00:20:55,330 --> 00:20:58,290
I know everything, and I'm mad at you.

238
00:20:58,290 --> 00:21:01,140
I know things will get boring and obvious,

239
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:06,270
but I like you so much that I'm going mad.

240
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:16,150
I like you.

241
00:21:20,130 --> 00:21:22,160
So, don't go.

242
00:21:24,020 --> 00:21:26,270
As long as I'm with you,

243
00:21:26,270 --> 00:21:28,460
everything is fine.

244
00:21:30,910 --> 00:21:33,010
I still like you.

245
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:37,460
Kim Min Joon,

246
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:45,150
you can't get away from me.

247
00:21:46,790 --> 00:21:49,210
I'll make sure you don't feel lonely anymore.

248
00:21:50,950 --> 00:21:52,960
Let's take everything slowly.

249
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:56,420
♫ <i>All the pieces of these feelings</i> ♫

250
00:21:56,420 --> 00:22:01,070
♫ <i>Are coming to me when I'm lost</i> ♫

251
00:22:01,070 --> 00:22:06,630
♫ <i>I hope I don't think of you while sleeping lightly</i> ♫

252
00:22:06,630 --> 00:22:12,680
♫ <i>I'm sorry I can't give you as much</i> ♫

253
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,820
♫ <i>I really am</i> ♫

254
00:22:14,820 --> 00:22:17,810
♫ <i>All of your words...</i> ♫

255
00:22:17,810 --> 00:22:19,540
[Epilogue]
What about work?

256
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:21,430
I took the rest of the day off.

257
00:22:24,040 --> 00:22:25,570
Choi Jin Hwan.

258
00:22:25,570 --> 00:22:26,900
Yes?

259
00:22:28,020 --> 00:22:31,690
If I had asked you...

260
00:22:31,690 --> 00:22:34,090
without avoiding it back then,

261
00:22:34,090 --> 00:22:36,030
would we have been different?

262
00:22:40,490 --> 00:22:42,650
I'm not sure.

263
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:46,880
But we should only focus on now.

264
00:22:48,040 --> 00:22:50,730
The fact that we're together is important.

265
00:22:56,210 --> 00:22:58,850
You're mean. I'm mad at you.

